{"tid":137632,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人好鍾意一個人睇戲?","createTime":"2017-02-28T03:25:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-28T09:34:16.000Z","uid":74692,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"397412312d7757a9bb3e521b566f69658e065ff0","tid":137632,"uid":74692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T03:25:48.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n小弟鍾意間唔中就自己一個去睇下戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔係話同fd睇唔好<br />\n但一黎有時時間就唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一黎有d fd又好撚鍾意係到邊睇邊傾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n試過有次睇美隊3<br />\n條撚樣一睇到爆炸畫面就係到配音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係到哇哇哇 轟呀 <br />\n我當堂屌撚左出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n心諗你要配音就買碟返屋企自己配撚飽佢啦屌<br />\n<br />\n之後就好少約人睇戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n前日去睇戲<br />\n個mk妹問我幾多個人睇<br />\n我話一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢即刻呆左呆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 之後拍一拍佢同事<br />\n問佢 喂 你會唔會一個人睇戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n屌你老母 依加一個人睇戲都唔撚俾咩仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁多位巴打絲打會唔會自己一個人睇戲?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f77424986d56b9190d8d97257331465a4afb6ad1","tid":137632,"uid":56836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T03:29:10.000Z","msg":"會啊<br />\n一直以來都覺得根本睇戲係一個人嘅活動<br />\n<br />\n又唔使溝通，係自己個腦對套戲嘅交流<br />\n<br />\n同訓覺一樣，有人陪可以，冇人陪都唔影響，如果旁邊個人打鼻鼾嘈倒你就影響埋你。。。<br />\n<br />\n係唔知點解啲人會覺得自己一個睇好毒姐..."},{"pid":"8e4ec42127041144ba4181b73f075e40a04d211f","tid":137632,"uid":9863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T03:31:28.000Z","msg":"喺屋企自己睇算唔算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"051972842fa18c4ac03cc13c168825cdeba74736","tid":137632,"uid":49178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T03:34:15.000Z","msg":"Plan 左今日自己睇 Lala land <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"794a840344bb99187065305404c33ad077349d00","tid":137632,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T03:35:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  舒服自在"},{"pid":"4bae4f07baab25901732d6c2243dcadee80cdb1c","tid":137632,"uid":25496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T03:37:02.000Z","msg":"本來就應該係個人活動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8ffc5d923f8a6a7c35d858b78d4664c54e048b0","tid":137632,"uid":21126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T03:42:21.000Z","msg":"通常一個月一個人入3-4次戲院<br />\n仲要揀前面已經冇哂人個行<br />\n好享受個種好似包左場既感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae43c7b4444a313a01f615093ed77c5aaec1a527","tid":137632,"uid":74692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T03:43:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>喺屋企自己睇算唔算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔算<br />\n入戲院既先算"},{"pid":"f478c75db76165f8b2a4c6cfc3c6c92771589e71","tid":137632,"uid":9863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T04:37:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>喺屋企自己睇算唔算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔算<br />\n入戲院既先算</blockquote><br />\n咁真係未試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可以試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c0431d2f84f8079507c39eafafc88cc9c51507d","tid":137632,"uid":73064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T04:41:24.000Z","msg":"上次專登晨早起身<br />\n食埋個靚早餐去德福睇你的名字同鋼鋸嶺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  1點幾睇到5點半返歸<br />\n個職員都望住我呆左下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1056b9177011b430041be9498138d6ae7e8771f4","tid":137632,"uid":29601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T04:51:14.000Z","msg":"與其嘥時間約人又未必約得成 人哋又未必啱睇 寧願自己一個人睇 好舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f23425c4f6742b857ec3fd6e3f2e27316c4d1505","tid":137632,"uid":74692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T09:23:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />推"},{"pid":"6e89fc07e6926c79948c70f31afbc42ffcd8cfdf","tid":137632,"uid":28769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T09:25:59.000Z","msg":"超過3,4年未試過同人睇戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2d4277aeaed081dccca50464c3afe753b317293","tid":137632,"uid":22376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T09:28:42.000Z","msg":"識睇一定自己單機睇"},{"pid":"f26e2e00eb92a66724f9f799e6051c0800619266","tid":137632,"uid":8598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T09:29:44.000Z","msg":"最近睇早場試過幾次<br />\n<br />\n七俠蕩寇誌 太空潛航者 你的名字<br />\n<br />\n同班妹吓妹吓一齊睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6686dad42a207c5c614c11c8b3b02b1f6bdf7af3","tid":137632,"uid":74692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T09:30:24.000Z","msg":"啱呀屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但成日d人見你一個人睇 覺得你好慘咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌 我一個人睇關你撚事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10dbc34ee7e201b7b25bc7d2330e5625f8178da9","tid":137632,"uid":25855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T09:31:18.000Z","msg":"試過幾次，通常都會投入好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b28f883c601d7ebd6fbeaf5f0f193fe18dc7e939","tid":137632,"uid":85073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T09:34:16.000Z","msg":"你的名字真係好啱一個人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一個人睇戲真係易投入好多，唔使顧慮旁人鍾意笑就笑喊就喊，勁爽"}]}